data.description: Exceptional 4-bedroom, 3-full bath, with study and game room. Spacious and well-designed this home offers a secondary bedroom and full bath on the first floor.  Perfect blend of comfort and function. An open-concept layout connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an ideal space for spending quality time with guests and family.  The Kitchen features beautiful quartz counters and island seating.  The primary bedroom suite is a true sanctuary, offering a spacious haven for relaxation.  Bath is complete with a luxurious soaking tub, dual sinks, and a walk-in shower.  A covered patio overlooks the large backyard featuring an adjacent wooded area. Fosters Ridge offers a Rec Center, Pool, and a Playground and is located a few miles from I-45 off of 1488 and Old Conroe Road. Easy access to The Woodlands, Restaurants, Shopping Centers and Healthcare Facilities. Located within the highly rated Conroe ISD-Woodlands school system.  Schedule your tour today!
